{
  "stem": "4113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't wear an arm band.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That meant risking, you know, being shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said he was from Boynton, which is Bytom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Boynton was Germany now-- I mean then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he had heard from reliable authority that by the end of the year, there would be no Jews alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How he knew it, of course, now we know today, you know, that the Wannsee Conference at which place it was decided to kill all the Jews had taken place a few months earlier.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "How we knew it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he worked for the Germans there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, why don't we find a hiding place, because he would like to join us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember my father and my mother-- we talked about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know is he Jewish or is he a spy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We afraid.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's number one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How can you trust him?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Number two, who could imagine that you can kill millions of people?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It didn't make sense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, we have seen sporadic killing here and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But how-- how they kill millions?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No one believed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No one believed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So about a few months later, the order came to build a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, all Jews living outside would have to move into the ghetto, including us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We would have to go into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They took a small street, the Franciscan Street, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Francizkansa, ?] and blocked it off on either side, put the gate in, boarded up the windows to the outside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And all Jews were to move in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they put a Polish policemen and a Jewish policeman at the gate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you couldn't leave-- go and come without a special permit if you worked for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
